 padding: 4px 2px 0px; word-break: break-all;\">url</code>&nbsp;中，来获取我们的&nbsp;<code style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; font-family: Consolas, Inconsolata, Courier, monospace; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(199, 37, 78); background-color: rgb(249, 242, 244); border-radius: 2px; padding: 4px 2px 0px; word-break: break-all;\">id</code>&nbsp;然后根据这个&nbsp;<code style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; font-family: Consolas, Inconsolata, Courier, monospace; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(199, 37, 78); background-color: rgb(249, 242, 244); border-radius: 2px; padding: 4px 2px 0px; word-break: break-all;\">id</code>&nbsp;来进行数据的查询。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">好，想起来了。那么我们已经在&nbsp;<code style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; font-family: Consolas, Inconsolata, Courier, monospace; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(199, 37, 78); background-color: rgb(249, 242, 244); border-radius: 2px; padding: 4px 2px 0px; word-break: break-all;\">url</code>&nbsp;包含了这个&nbsp;<code style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; font-family: Consolas, Inconsolata, Courier, monospace; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(199, 37, 78); background-color: rgb(249, 242, 244); border-radius: 2px; padding: 4px 2px 0px; word-break: break-all;\">id</code>&nbsp;了。</p><pre class=\"prettyprint\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 8px 16px 4px 56px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 24px; position: relative; overflow-y: hidden; overflow-x: auto; font-family: Consolas, Inconsolata, Courier, monospace; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px; word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(246, 248, 250); border: none;\">http://localhost:8080/#/content/58eee565a92d341e48cfe7fc1</pre><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">如上：<code style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; font-family: Consolas, Inconsolata, Courier, monospace; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(199, 37, 78); background-color: rgb(249, 242, 244); border-radius: 2px; padding: 4px 2px 0px; word-break: break-all;\">58eee565a92d341e48cfe7fc</code>&nbsp;这个就是&nbsp;<code style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; font-family: Consolas, Inconsolata, Courier, monospace; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(199, 37, 78); background-color: rgb(249, 242, 244); border-radius: 2px; padding: 4px 2px 0px; word-break: break-all;\">ID</code>&nbsp;，奇怪是奇怪了点，但确实就是&nbsp;<code style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; font-family: Consolas, Inconsolata, Courier, monospace; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(199, 37, 78); background-color: rgb(249, 242, 244); border-radius: 2px; padding: 4px 2px 0px; word-break: break-all;\">id</code>。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">我们如何取出来呢？</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">不用想很多复杂的事情，<code style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; font-family: Consolas, Inconsolata, Courier, monospace; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(199, 37, 78); background-color: rgb(249, 242, 244); border-radius: 2px; padding: 4px 2px 0px; word-break: break-all;\">vuerouter</code>&nbsp;早就给我们准备了解决方法了。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">我们可以在项目中打印如下代码：</p><pre class=\"prettyprint\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 8px 16px 4px 56px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 24px; position: relative; overflow-y: hidden; overflow-x: auto; font-family: Consolas, Inconsolata, Courier, monospace; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px; word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(246, 248, 250); border: none;\">console.log(this.$route)1</pre><blockquote style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 16px; margin: 0px 0px 24px; border-left: 8px solid rgb(221, 223, 228); background: rgb(238, 240, 244); overflow: auto; word-wrap: normal; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;\"><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); line-height: 22px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all;\">擦，博客写到这里&nbsp;<code style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; font-family: Consolas, Inconsolata, Courier, monospace; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(199, 37, 78); background-color: rgb(249, 242, 244); border-radius: 2px; padding: 4px 2px 0px; word-break: break-all;\">cnodejs.org</code>&nbsp;网站挂了。。。那就暂时不放我的打印结果图了，大家可以看下官方文档&nbsp;<a href=\"https://router.vuejs.org/zh-cn/api/route-object.html#%E8%B7%AF%E7%94%B1%E4%BF%A1%E6%81%AF%E5%AF%B9%E8%B1%A1%E7%9A%84%E5%B1%9E%E6%80%A7\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; color: rgb(103, 149, 181); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; word-break: break-all;\">路由信息对象的属性</a></p></blockquote><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">回头，你也可以自己打印了看下，有助于你自己分析理解问题。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">好了，除了上面的问题，我们再看下我们的接口数据调用，代码如下：</p><pre class=\"prettyprint\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 8px 16px 4px 56px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 24px; position: relative; overflow-y: hidden; overflow-x: auto; font-family: Consolas, Inconsolata, Courier, monospace; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px; word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(246, 248, 250); border: none;\">this.$api.get(&#39;topic/&#39;&nbsp;+&nbsp;this.id,&nbsp;null,&nbsp;r&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;{&nbsp;&nbsp;this.dat&nbsp;=&nbsp;r.data\n})123</pre><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">等于没什么要说的，就是把数据拿过来了而已，需要注意的是，我们的请求的接口地址是根据&nbsp;<code style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; font-family: Consolas, Inconsolata, Courier, monospace; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(199, 37, 78); background-color: rgb(249, 242, 244); border-radius: 2px; padding: 4px 2px 0px; word-break: break-all;\">id</code>&nbsp;进行变化的。所以，我这边采用了字符串拼接的方法，<code style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; font-family: Consolas, Inconsolata, Courier, monospace; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(199, 37, 78); background-color: rgb(249, 242, 244); border-radius: 2px; padding: 4px 2px 0px; word-break: break-all;\">&#39;topic/&#39; + this.id</code>&nbsp;来得到我们真正想要请求的接口数据。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">好，到这里为止，我们已经非常顺利的把列表页面和内容页面已经渲染出来了。希望你也成功了！</p><blockquote style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 16px; margin: 0px 0px 24px; border-left: 8px solid rgb(221, 223, 228); background: rgb(238, 240, 244); overflow: auto; word-wrap: normal; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;\"><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); line-height: 22px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all;\">如果文章由于我学识浅薄，导致您发现有严重谬误的地方，请一定在评论中指出，我会在第一时间修正我的博文，以避免误人子弟。</p></blockquote><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">本文由 FungLeo 原创，允许转载，但转载必须保留首发链接。</p><p><br/></p>', '2018-06-09 18:20:55', '2018-06-09 18:20:55', '1', '2', '1', '0');
INSERT INTO `forum` VALUES ('15', '深入浅出理解HOG特征---梯度方向直方图', '<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">梯度方向直方图&nbsp;<br/>原文路径：<a href=\"https://www.learnopencv.com/histogram-of-oriented-gradients/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; color: rgb(103, 149, 181); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; word-break: break-all;\">https://www.learnopencv.com/histogram-of-oriented-gradients/</a></p><h2 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 8px 0px 16px; font-size: 24px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; color: rgb(78, 161, 219); cursor: pointer; word-break: break-all;\"></a>最近在搞车牌识别的时候，训练样本去识别车牌的时候用到HOG特征。国外一篇文章让我受益良多</h2><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">什么是特征描述符？&nbsp;<br/>特征描述符是指通过提取有用的信息并抛弃无关的信息来表示这一张图片或者一张图片的一部分</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">典型地，特征描述符将大小宽度x高度x 3（通道）的图像转换为特征向量数组，长度n。例如：在HOG特征描述器的情况下，输入图像大小为64×128×3，输出特征向量长度为3780。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">【&nbsp;<br/>中间有一个循环装箱的过程&nbsp;<br/>划分为8x8大小的图像补丁块处理，装到9个箱子（其中8x8、9 这些参数都是不固定的，但是是推荐的）&nbsp;<br/>移动步伐：8个像素&nbsp;<br/>width:64 /8 == 8 份&nbsp;<br/>Height:128 /8 ==16份&nbsp;<br/>用一个16x16的窗口来处理，可以包含4个8X8的图像补丁，那么处理一次会有得到4*9个箱子数据。循环处理&nbsp;<br/>最后能循环 7*15=105次&nbsp;<br/>105*36=3780个箱子数据，存储的是每个像素的梯度大小和梯度方向&nbsp;<br/>】</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">记住，HOG特征描述符能够用其他的尺寸大小来计算，但是在下面的具体例子里为了让你更加容易理解相关概念，选择使用图像宽高：64×128，图像补丁 8x8 窗口 16X16 移动步长 8个像素</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">首先来了解什么是“有用的信息”、什么是“无关的信息”？我们需要明确知道“有用”是指对什么有用。&nbsp;<br/>特征向量对查看图像是没有用的，但是，对于图像识别和目标检测这些任务是非常有用的。将这些算法生成的特征向量引入到支持向量机（SVM）等图像分类算法中，可以取得不错的效果。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">但是，哪一种“特征”对分类任务才是真正有用的呢？让我们用一个例子来讨论这一点。 假设我们要建立一个物体检测仪，用来检测衬衫和大衣的纽扣。按钮是圆形的（在图像中可能看起来是椭圆的），通常有几个洞用于缝纫。 你可以在一个按钮的图像上运行一个边缘检测器，只需简单地观察边缘图像就可以很容易地判断它是否是一个按钮。在这种情况下，边缘信息是“有用的”，而颜色信息不是。 此外，该功能还需要有鉴别能力。例如，从图像中提取的良好特征应该能够分辨按钮和其他圆形物体，如硬币和汽车轮胎的区别。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">在HOG特征描述器中，梯度方向（梯度）的分布（直方图）作为特征。 图像的梯度（x和y导数）是有用的，因为梯度的大小在边缘和拐角处（突然强度变化的区域）很大，而且我们知道边和角在物体形状上的信息比平面区域要多得多。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">怎么去计算方向梯度直方图？&nbsp;<br/>在这一节中，我们将深入研究计算HOG特征描述符的细节。为了说明每一步，我们将使用一个图像块。</p><h2 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 8px 0px 16px; font-size: 24px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; color: rgb(78, 161, 219); cursor: pointer; word-break: break-all;\"></a>步骤1：预处理</h2><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">如前所述的HOG特征描述符用于行人检测，是在64×128片图像计算。当然，图像可能是任意大小的。通常在多个尺度上分析多个图像位置，唯一的限制是被分析的补丁具有固定的长宽比（纵横比）。在我们的例子中，补丁需要有一个长宽比为1:2。例如，他们可以100×200, 128×256，或1000×2000而不是101×205。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">为了说明这一点，下面展示了一个大尺寸的720×475图像。我们计算我们的HOG特征描述符选择一块大小100×200。这个补丁被裁剪的图像并调整其大小以64×128。现在已经准备好计算这个图像补丁的HOG描述符了。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img title=\"\" alt=\"这里写图片描述\" src=\"/ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20180609/1528539716567059451.png\"/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">还有一个预处理步骤就是“伽玛校正”，但性能提升非常小，所以这里跳过该步骤。</p><h2 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 8px 0px 16px; font-size: 24px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; color: rgb(78, 161, 219); cursor: pointer; word-break: break-all;\"></a>步骤2：计算图像梯度</h2><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">要计算一个HOG描述符，我们首先需要计算水平和垂直梯度；毕竟，我们要计算梯度直方图。通过用以下内核过滤图像很容易做到这一点。&nbsp;<br/><img title=\"\" alt=\"这里写图片描述\" src=\"/ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20180609/1528539717083093918.png\"/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">我们可以在opencv中使用内核大小为1的Sobel算子实现同样的结果。</p><pre class=\"prettyprint\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 8px 16px 4px 56px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 24px; position: relative; overflow-y: hidden; overflow-x: auto; font-family: Consolas, Inconsolata, Courier, monospace; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px; word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(246, 248, 250); border: none;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;//&nbsp;Read&nbsp;image\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Mat&nbsp;img&nbsp;=&nbsp;imread(&quot;F:/data/car/test1.jpg&quot;);\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;img.convertTo(img,&nbsp;CV_32F,&nbsp;1&nbsp;/&nbsp;255.0);&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;//&nbsp;Calculate&nbsp;gradients&nbsp;gx,&nbsp;gy\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Mat&nbsp;gx,&nbsp;gy;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;//对X梯度绝对值\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Sobel(img,&nbsp;gx,&nbsp;CV_32F,&nbsp;1,&nbsp;0,&nbsp;1);&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;//对Y梯度绝对值\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Sobel(img,&nbsp;gy,&nbsp;CV_32F,&nbsp;0,&nbsp;1,&nbsp;1);12345678910</pre><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">接下来，我们可以用下面的公式找到梯度的大小和方向</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img title=\"\" alt=\"这里写图片描述\" src=\"/ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20180609/1528539717638049398.png\"/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">如果你是使用opencv，计算梯度的大小和方向可以使用函数carttopolar，如下所示。</p><pre class=\"prettyprint\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 8px 16px 4px 56px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 24px; position: relative; overflow-y: hidden; overflow-x: auto; font-family: Consolas, Inconsolata, Courier, monospace; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px; word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(246, 248, 250); border: none;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Mat&nbsp;mag,&nbsp;angle;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;//mag&nbsp;坡度梯度&nbsp;大小\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;//mag就是大小&nbsp;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;//angle就是方向\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;cartToPolar(gx,&nbsp;gy,&nbsp;mag,&nbsp;angle,&nbsp;1);12345</pre><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">下图显示了梯度</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img title=\"\" alt=\"这里写图片描述\" src=\"/ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20180609/1528539718091060419.png\"/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">注意，图x梯度在垂直线方向延伸，图y-梯度在水平线方向延伸。图坡度梯度在强度上有急剧的变化。当图片区域光滑时，都没有延伸。我故意遗漏了显示渐变方向的图像，因为作为图像显示的方向不能传达太多信息。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">注意看图像的变化&nbsp;<br/>渐变图像去除了许多非必要的信息（例如恒定的彩色背景），但突出显示了轮廓。换句话说，你可以看到渐变图像，并且很容易地辨别出图片中有一个人。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">图x梯度 注意水平方向基本没有延伸&nbsp;<br/>图y梯度 注意垂直方向基本没有延伸</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img title=\"\" alt=\"这里写图片描述\" src=\"/ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20180609/1528539719148043161.png\"/></p><h2 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 8px 0px 16px; font-size: 24px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; color: rgb(78, 161, 219); cursor: pointer; word-break: break-all;\"></a>步骤3：计算在8×8细胞梯度直方图</h2><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">在这一步中，图像被分为8×8细胞和梯度直方图计算每个8×8细胞。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img title=\"\" alt=\"这里写图片描述\" src=\"/ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20180609/1528539720044095894.png\"/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">我们将学习了解在一瞬间的直方图，但是在我们去之前就让我们先了解为什么我们把图像分为8×8细胞。使用特征描述符描述图像补丁的一个重要原因是它提供了一个紧凑的表示。8×8图像补丁包含8x8x3 = 192像素值。这个补丁梯度每像素包含2个值（大小和方向），那就变成8x8x2 = 128个数。通过这一部分的最后我们会看到这128个数字是用9-bin直方图(可存储为长度9的数组，通俗地说是分别装到9个箱子里)表示。不仅是表示更简洁，计算在补丁直方图具有更强的健壮性。个别的颜色梯度可能有噪音，但用一个8x8图像补丁来表示梯度直方图对噪声不敏感，换句话说，就是受噪音影响不大。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">但是什么是8x8图像补丁？为什么不是32x32？这是我们通过特征缩放来寻找到的明确的选择。HOG最初用于检测行人。在一张行人照片缩放到64×128，使用8×8细胞足以捕捉有趣的功能（如面部、头部的等）。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">让我们看一个8×8补丁在图像梯度的面貌</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img title=\"\" alt=\"这里写图片描述\" src=\"/ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20180609/1528539720432074226.png\"/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">中间的图像信息量是非常大的。它显示了用箭头表示梯度的图像的贴片，箭头显示梯度的方向，其长度显示大小。注意箭头的方向如何指向强度的变化方向，其大小表示差异的大小。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">在右边，我们看到原始的数字表示在8×8细胞有一个小的差异，那就是角度是0度和180度的梯度，而不是0到360度之间。这些被称为“无符号”渐变，因为梯度正值和它的负值用相同的数字表示。换句话说，梯度箭头和与之相对的180度箭头被认为是相同的。但是，为什么不使用0 - 360度呢？经验表明，无符号梯度比签名梯度更好地用于行人检测。HOG的一些实现将允许您指定是否使用带符号的渐变。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">下一步是创建一个8×8细胞梯度直方图。直方图包含9个箱子对应角度0, 20, 40…160。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">下图说明了这个过程。我们正在前面的图寻找在同8×8补丁梯度的幅值和方向。根据方向选择箱子，并根据大小选择投票（进入箱子的值）。让我们首先关注环绕在蓝色中的像素。它的角度（方向）为80度，大小为2。所以它放入到第五个箱子。用红色包围的像素的梯度方向为10度，大小为4。由于10度是0和20之间的一半，所以像素的也是均匀地分成两个箱子。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img title=\"\" alt=\"这里写图片描述\" src=\"/ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20180609/1528539721068003912.png\"/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">还有一个细节需要注意。如果角度大于160度，则在160到180之间，我们知道角度绕成0和180相等。因此，在下面的例子中，角度为165度的像素正比于0度的箱子和160度的箱子。&nbsp;<br/>从160-180&nbsp;<br/>180-165/165-160=3&nbsp;<br/>所以0箱子分4/1，160箱子分4/3</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">在8×8细胞中所有像素的贡献加起来创造9-bin直方图。对于上面的补丁，它看起来像这样</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img title=\"\" alt=\"这里写图片描述\" src=\"/ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20180609/1528539721324075018.png\"/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">在我们的表示中，y轴是0度。你可以看到直方图在0度和180度附近占很大比重。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img title=\"\" alt=\"这里写图片描述\" src=\"/ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20180609/1528539721708032880.png\"/></p><h2 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 8px 0px 16px; font-size: 24px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; color: rgb(78, 161, 219); cursor: pointer; word-break: break-all;\"></a>步骤4：16x16步块归一化</h2><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">在前面的步骤中，我们根据图像的梯度创建了一个直方图。图像的梯度对整体亮度是敏感的。如果通过将所有像素值除以2来使图像变暗，则渐变幅度将改变一半，因此直方图值将改变一半。理想情况下，我们希望描述符不受光照变化的影响。换句话说，我们希望使直方图正常化(归一化)，这样它们不会受到光照变化的影响。&nbsp;<br/>在解释直方图是如何规范化之前，让我们看看长度为3的向量是如何规范化的。&nbsp;<br/><img title=\"\" alt=\"这里写图片描述\" src=\"/ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20180609/1528539722029030538.png\"/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">例如：一个像素向量RGB【128,64,32】，向量的长度则为：sqrt{128^2 + 64^2 + 32^2} = 146.64&nbsp;<br/>这也被称为向量的L2范数。将向量的每一个元素除以146.64得到归一化向量【0.87,0.43,0.22】，可以看到，归一化后的【256,128,32】将得到【0.87,0.43,0.22】可以看到归一化向量消除了规模。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">现在我们知道了如何归一化一个矢量，你可能会认为在计算HOG特征时可以将9x1的直方图以上述的3×1矢量的方式归一化。可以是可以，但更好的办法是归一化一个更大尺寸的16×16块。16×16块用4个直方图可级联成一个36×1元矢量，使用3×1矢量归一化的方法。然后通过8像素的窗口移动（见动画）重复计算，归一化的36×1向量。</p><h2 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 8px 0px 16px; font-size: 24px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; color: rgb(78, 161, 219); cursor: pointer; word-break: break-all;\"></a>步骤5：计算HOG特征向量</h2><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">计算整个图像补丁最终的特征向量，36×1载体连接成一个巨大的载体。这个向量的大小是多少？&nbsp;<br/>原图截取100*200—&gt;resize—&gt;64*128&nbsp;<br/>64/8=8&nbsp;<br/>128/8=16&nbsp;<br/>1、我们有多少个16×16块吗？有7个水平和15个垂直位置，总共7×15＝105个块。&nbsp;<br/>2、每16×16块由36×1矢量表示。所以当我们连接成一个巨大的载体，他们都得到了36×105 = 3780维向量。</p><h2 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 8px 0px 16px; font-size: 24px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 32px; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; color: rgb(78, 161, 219); cursor: pointer; word-break: break-all;\"></a>定向梯度直方图的可视化</h2><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img title=\"\" alt=\"这里写图片描述\" src=\"/ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20180609/1528539722363084867.png\"/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">一个图像块的HOG特征描述符通常是通过在8×8组织的9×1归一化直方图可视化。见上图像。你会注意到，直方图的主导方向捕捉人的形状，特别是围绕躯干和腿。&nbsp;<br/>不幸的是，没有简单的方法来可视化OpenCV的HOG描述符。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">至此：翻译完成，英语水平有限，有错误的地方，希望不吝赐教。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">笔者：&nbsp;<br/>下一篇博客会用C++、Opencv、支持SVM向量机来训练提取HOG特征。</p><p><br/></p>', '2018-06-09 18:22:37', '2018-06-09 18:22:37', '1', '2', '1', '0');
INSERT INTO `forum` VALUES ('16', 'Appium移动自动化框架初探', '<article><h5 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 8px 0px 16px; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; word-break: break-all;\">作者：cryanimal QQ:164166060</h5><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all;\">本文简要介绍了appnium自动化框架的架构、加载流程、支持语言、相关配置，以及元素定位工具等。</p><h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 8px 0px 16px; font-size: 22px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 30px; word-break: break-all;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; color: rgb(78, 161, 219); cursor: pointer; word-break: break-all;\"></a>官方网站：</h3><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all;\"><a href=\"http://appium.io/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; color: rgb(103, 149, 181); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; word-break: break-all;\">http://appium.io</a></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all;\"><a href=\"http://images2015.cnblogs.com/blog/968033/201606/968033-20160622111442344-1855722972.png\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; color: rgb(103, 149, 181); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; word-break: break-all;\"><img src=\"http://images2015.cnblogs.com/blog/968033/201606/968033-20160622111443828-356851408.png\" alt=\"image\" title=\"image\"/></a></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all;\">Appnium是由SauceLabs支持，一家业界领先的测试产品公司, 有成熟的企业测试解决方案</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all;\">&nbsp;</p><h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 8px 0px 16px; font-size: 22px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 30px; word-break: break-all;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; color: rgb(78, 161, 219); cursor: pointer; word-break: break-all;\"></a>Appium支持的平台</h3><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all;\"><a href=\"http://images2015.cnblogs.com/blog/968033/201606/968033-20160622111444641-1762387238.png\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; color: rgb(103, 149, 181); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; word-break: break-all;\"><img src=\"http://images2015.cnblogs.com/blog/968033/201606/968033-20160622111445156-899657725.png\" alt=\"image\" title=\"image\"/></a></p><ul style=\"list-style-type: none;\" class=\" list-paddingleft-2\"><li><p>Android上使用了instrumentation和uiautomator两套技术</p></li><li><p>iOS使用uiautomation</p></li><li><p>同时还支持firefox, 并可扩展其他平台</p></li></ul><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all;\">&nbsp;</p><h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 8px 0px 16px; font-size: 22px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 30px; word-break: break-all;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; color: rgb(78, 161, 219); cursor: pointer; word-break: break-all;\"></a>Appium的优点</h3><ul style=\"list-style-type: none;\" class=\" list-paddingleft-2\"><li><p>跨架构，native hybrid webview</p></li><li><p>跨设备，android iosfirefoxos</p></li><li><p>跨语言，java python ruby nodejsphp</p></li><li><p>跨app, 可以在多个app之间交互</p></li><li><p>不依赖源代码</p></li><li><p>不限制测试框架和平台</p></li></ul><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all;\">&nbsp;</p><h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 8px 0px 16px; font-size: 22px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 30px; word-break: break-all;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; color: rgb(78, 161, 219); cursor: pointer; word-break: break-all;\"></a>Appium在Android上的架构</h3><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all;\"><a href=\"http://images2015.cnblogs.com/blog/968033/201606/968033-20160622111445922-1688525852.png\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; color: rgb(103, 149, 181); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; word-break: break-all;\"><img src=\"http://images2015.cnblogs.com/blog/968033/201606/968033-20160622111447125-1344324253.png\" alt=\"image\" title=\"image\"/></a></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all;\">&nbsp;</p><h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 8px 0px 16px; font-size: 22px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 30px; word-break: break-all;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; color: rgb(78, 161, 219); cursor: pointer; word-break: break-all;\"></a>Appium在iOS上的架构</h3><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all;\"><a href=\"http://images2015.cnblogs.com/blog/968033/201606/968033-20160622111448750-1613658397.png\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; color: rgb(103, 149, 181); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; word-break: break-all;\"><img src=\"http://images2015.cnblogs.com/blog/968033/201606/968033-20160622111449735-641745632.png\" alt=\"image\" title=\"image\"/></a></p><h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 8px 0px 16px; font-size: 22px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 30px; word-break: break-all;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; color: rgb(78, 161, 219); cursor: pointer; word-break: break-all;\"></a>Appium的安装</h3><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all;\">详见：<a href=\"http://blog.csdn.net/kaka1121/article/details/51698700\" title=\"http://blog.csdn.net/kaka1121/article/details/51698700\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; color: rgb(103, 149, 181); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; word-break: break-all;\">http://blog.csdn.net/kaka1121/article/details/51698700</a></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all;\">Appium的启动，上文中也有详解</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all;\">通过命令：Appium–help 可以看到一些可选参数</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all;\">默认开启4723端口接受webdriver请求&nbsp;<br/>默认开启4724用于和android通讯</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all;\">视频演示：<a href=\"http://v.youku.com/v_show/id_XNjM0ODIxNTUy.html\" title=\"http://v.youku.com/v_show/id_XNjM0ODIxNTUy.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; color: rgb(103, 149, 181); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; word-break: break-all;\">http://v.youku.com/v_show/id_XNjM0ODIxNTUy.html</a></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all;\">&nbsp;</p><h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 8px 0px 16px; font-size: 22px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 30px; word-break: break-all;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; color: rgb(78, 161, 219); cursor: pointer; word-break: break-all;\"></a>Appium自动化所需工具及android开发环境安装</h3><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all;\">依赖工具包括uiautomatorviewer、abd、DDMS等</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all;\">详见：<a href=\"http://blog.csdn.net/kaka1121/article/details/51698745\" title=\"http://blog.csdn.net/kaka1121/article/details/51698745\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; color: rgb(103, 149, 181); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; word-break: break-all;\">http://blog.csdn.net/kaka1121/article/details/51698745</a></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all;\">&nbsp;</p><h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 8px 0px 16px; font-size: 22px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 30px; word-break: break-all;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; color: rgb(78, 161, 219); cursor: pointer; word-break: break-all;\"></a>Appium的加载流程</h3><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all;\"><a href=\"http://images2015.cnblogs.com/blog/968033/201606/968033-20160622111450828-92209457.png\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; color: rgb(103, 149, 181); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; word-break: break-all;\"><img src=\"http://images2015.cnblogs.com/blog/968033/201606/968033-20160622111452297-1265726325.png\" alt=\"image\" title=\"image\"/></a></p><h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 8px 0px 16px; font-size: 22px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 30px; word-break: break-all;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; color: rgb(78, 161, 219); cursor: pointer; word-break: break-all;\"></a>Appium支持主流语言</h3><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all;\"><a href=\"http://images2015.cnblogs.com/blog/968033/201606/968033-20160622111453235-1212952422.png\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; color: rgb(103, 149, 181); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; word-break: break-all;\"><img src=\"http://images2015.cnblogs.com/blog/968033/201606/968033-20160622111453938-744976220.png\" alt=\"image\" title=\"image\"/></a></p><h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 8px 0px 16px; font-size: 22px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 30px; word-break: break-all;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; color: rgb(78, 161, 219); cursor: pointer; word-break: break-all;\"></a>Appium webdriver的capabilities配置</h3><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all;\">Capabilities是由客户端发送给Appium服务器端的用来告诉服务器去启动哪种我们想要的会话的一套键值对集合。当中也有一些键值对是用来在自动化的过程中修改服务器端的行为方式。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; font-weight: 700; word-break: break-all;\">必填的项目</span>：</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; font-weight: 700; word-break: break-all;\">deviceName ：</span>我无论填写什么值，在我机器上都可以跑通测试，但是这项又是必填。我用得Appium版本是V1.2.2。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; font-weight: 700; word-break: break-all;\">app&nbsp;</span>：如果填写了，appium会在目标机器上安装测试目标app，如果没有的话，会根据appActivity和appPackage去目标机器查找目标app</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; font-weight: 700; word-break: break-all;\">appPackage&nbsp;</span>: 可以通过sdk自带工具aapt获得</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all;\"><a href=\"http://images2015.cnblogs.com/blog/968033/201606/968033-20160622114347656-2073119899.png\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; color: rgb(103, 149, 181); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; word-break: break-all;\"><img src=\"http://images2015.cnblogs.com/blog/968033/201606/968033-20160622114354016-351078719.png\" alt=\"image\" title=\"image\"/></a></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; font-weight: 700; word-break: break-all;\">appActivity</span>:同样可以通过以上工具获得。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all;\">有一点需要注意的是，值可以附加packageName，也可以不附加。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all;\">也就是说以下两种填写方式都是对的“.NotesList”和”com.example.android.notepad.NotesList”</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; font-weight: 700; word-break: break-all;\">通用配置：</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all;\"><a href=\"http://images2015.cnblogs.com/blog/968033/201606/968033-20160622111454797-964740287.png\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; color: rgb(103, 149, 181); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; word-break: break-all;\"><img src=\"http://images2015.cnblogs.com/blog/968033/201606/968033-20160622111456000-1887631309.png\" alt=\"image\" title=\"image\"/></a></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; font-weight: 700; word-break: break-all;\">android only：</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all;\"><a href=\"http://images2015.cnblogs.com/blog/968033/201606/968033-20160622111457344-845053880.png\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; color: rgb(103, 149, 181); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; word-break: break-all;\"><img src=\"http://images2015.cnblogs.com/blog/968033/201606/968033-20160622111508703-2066390366.png\" alt=\"image\" title=\"image\"/></a></p><h5 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 8px 0px 16px; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; word-break: break-all;\">IOS ONLY</h5><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all;\"><a href=\"http://images2015.cnblogs.com/blog/968033/201606/968033-20160622111509735-1280223027.png\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; color: rgb(103, 149, 181); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; word-break: break-all;\"><img src=\"http://images2015.cnblogs.com/blog/968033/201606/968033-20160622111510594-1590471995.png\" alt=\"image\" title=\"image\"/></a></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all;\">配置原文参见：<a href=\"http://blog.sina.com.cn/s/blog_700be1c00102vgha.html\" title=\"http://blog.sina.com.cn/s/blog_700be1c00102vgha.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; color: rgb(103, 149, 181); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; word-break: break-all;\">http://blog.sina.com.cn/s/blog_700be1c00102vgha.html</a></p><h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 8px 0px 16px; font-size: 22px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 30px; word-break: break-all;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; color: rgb(78, 161, 219); cursor: pointer; word-break: break-all;\"></a>java Demo示例</h3><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all;\"><a href=\"http://images2015.cnblogs.com/blog/968033/201606/968033-20160622111511656-1013809357.png\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; color: rgb(103, 149, 181); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; word-break: break-all;\"><img src=\"http://images2015.cnblogs.com/blog/968033/201606/968033-20160622111512375-406876387.png\" alt=\"image\" title=\"image\"/></a></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all;\">详细情况，参见我的另一篇博文</p><h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 8px 0px 16px; font-size: 22px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 30px; word-break: break-all;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; color: rgb(78, 161, 219); cursor: pointer; word-break: break-all;\"></a>元素定位</h3><ul style=\"list-style-type: none;\" class=\" list-paddingleft-2\"><li><p>Android和iOS的原生控件以及webview控件映射为特定的命名, 比如把所有平台的按钮映射为button元素</p></li><li><p>把当前的结构树映射为html文档</p></li><li><p>通过xpath来选择元素</p></li></ul><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all;\">三种定位方式</p><ul style=\"list-style-type: none;\" class=\" list-paddingleft-2\"><li><p>Name: id，label text</p></li><li><p>Tag_name: component type</p></li><li><p>Xpath</p></li></ul><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all;\">查看元素的属性以及xpath，使用uiautomatorview</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all;\"><a href=\"http://images2015.cnblogs.com/blog/968033/201606/968033-20160622111513406-221922643.png\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; color: rgb(103, 149, 181); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; word-break: break-all;\"><img src=\"http://images2015.cnblogs.com/blog/968033/201606/968033-20160622111515235-1342465444.png\" alt=\"image\" title=\"image\"/></a></p><h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 8px 0px 16px; font-size: 22px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 30px; word-break: break-all;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; color: rgb(78, 161, 219); cursor: pointer; word-break: break-all;\"></a>元素交互</h3><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all;\">Webdriver已经支持</p><ul style=\"list-style-type: none;\" class=\" list-paddingleft-2\"><li><p>点击</p></li><li><p>输入</p></li><li><p>按键事件</p></li></ul><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all;\">Mobile相关:</p><ul style=\"list-style-type: none;\" class=\" list-paddingleft-2\"><li><p>拖动</p></li><li><p>划动</p></li><li><p>长按</p></li></ul><h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 8px 0px 16px; font-size: 22px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 30px; word-break: break-all;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; color: rgb(78, 161, 219); cursor: pointer; word-break: break-all;\"></a>附录：业界top框架综合对比</h3><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all;\"><a href=\"http://images2015.cnblogs.com/blog/968033/201606/968033-20160622111517203-1037089926.png\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; color: rgb(103, 149, 181); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; word-break: break-all;\"><img src=\"http://images2015.cnblogs.com/blog/968033/201606/968033-20160622111518235-274131459.png\" alt=\"image\" title=\"image\"/></a></p></article><p>版权声明：本文为博主原创文章，未经博主允许不得转载。	https://blog.csdn.net/kaka1121/article/details/51732920</p><p><br/></p>', '2018-06-09 18:24:23', '2018-06-09 18:24:23', '1', '2', '0', '0');
INSERT INTO `forum` VALUES ('17', '人脸识别、姿态识别问题处理步骤', '<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">——-本文是参考王守佳先生的博士论文《基于图像的人体监测跟踪和人脸识别的研究》而写的笔记。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">对于模式识别问题，首先是必须对视频图像进行预处理，滤除杂波后，开始识别的步骤。目前人脸识别中光照预处理方法常用的有直方图均衡化（&nbsp;<br/>Histogram Equalization，HE）、Gamma 校正。局部对比度增强算法( Local Contrast Enhancement,LCE、离散余弦变换&nbsp;<br/>(Discrete Cosine Transform, DCT)以及高斯差分滤波算法（&nbsp;<br/>Difference of Gaussian filter，DOG等。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">第一步是前景分割，相关的算法在上一个博客中罗列了出来。&nbsp;<br/><a href=\"http://blog.csdn.net/qq_19764963/article/details/51198627\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; color: rgb(103, 149, 181); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; word-break: break-all;\">http://blog.csdn.net/qq_19764963/article/details/51198627</a></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">第二步是人体的识别，一般的思路是对运动前景进行特征提取，接着训练强分类器，利用分类器对之前提取的特征进行分类识别。常用的特征包括肤色颜色特征和人形轮廓特征。以下罗列常见的人体轮廓特征识别方法：&nbsp;<br/>2.1 整体特征识别，常用提取轮廓特征的方法包括：HOG特征，edgelet特征，小波特征，shapelet特征；&nbsp;<br/>2.2组合部位的识别，通过人体不同部位的识别组合，判断前景是否为人体，常用的方法包括：贝叶斯推断组合分类法，隐式模型法，自适应组合分类法；&nbsp;<br/>2.3多相机识别，通过多角度的到的图片综合判断识别，方法有 cluster boosted tree</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">第三步是目标跟踪，主要有几种思路：&nbsp;<br/>3.1基于区域的运动物体跟踪， 方法有&nbsp;<br/>Joint Probabilistic Data Association Filter&nbsp;<br/>3.2基于网格的运动物体跟踪&nbsp;<br/>3.3基于变形模板的运动物体跟踪&nbsp;<br/>3.4基于小波的运动物体跟踪&nbsp;<br/>3.5基于模型的运动物体跟踪&nbsp;<br/>3.6基于轮廓的运动物体跟踪&nbsp;<br/>3.7基于特征的运动物体跟踪&nbsp;<br/>另外，<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; font-weight: 700; word-break: break-all;\">粒子滤波和卡尔曼滤波</span>也有不错的效果。</p><p><br/></p>', '2018-06-09 18:25:11', '2018-06-09 18:25:11', '1', '2', '0', '0');
INSERT INTO `forum` VALUES ('18', '敏捷软件测试常见的七个误区', '<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 1.2em !important;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; line-height: 25.6px;\">转自 ThoughtWorks</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; line-height: 25.6px;\"></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all;\"><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 1.2em !important;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; line-height: 25.6px;\">敏捷软件开发是从1990年代开始逐渐引起广泛关注的一种新型软件开发方法，是能够应对快速变化的需求的一种软件开发能力，它作为一种新型的开发模式，被越来越多地应用到软件项目中。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 1.2em !important;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; line-height: 25.6px;\">敏捷软件测试指的是在敏捷软件开发过程中跟质量相关的一系列活动，和传统意义上的软件测试有很多区别，因为敏捷软件测试的概念一直比较模糊，所以经常会有人走入误区，我曾经在瀑布型的软件开发模式下做过几年的测试人员，所以在刚刚接触敏捷项目的时候也曾有过一些误解，但是在敏捷软件开发团队工作将近5年后，对很多问题有了新的认识，以下针对几个常见的误区和大家分享一下我的理解。</span></p><h5 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; word-break: break-all; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 1.2em !important;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; font-size: 1.3em;\">不需要测试策略</span></h5><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 1.2em !important;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; line-height: 25.6px;\">测试策略关注的是目标和方法，即怎样在限定的时间内有效利用有限的资源达到提前制定的目标，一般制定测试策略时会首先明确测试目标，然后确定需要哪些测试类型，各种测试类型所占的大概比例，选择测试框架，最后规划一下软件发布前需要经历哪些测试阶段。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 1.2em !important;\">很多人认为，敏捷软件开发以用户故事为单元，是不是集中精力在用户故事测试就足够了？是不是根本不需要考虑测试策略？</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 1.2em !important;\">其实这是一个很大的误解，因为敏捷软件开发通常都是迭代式的发布，周期比较短，资源非常有限，这就更需要我们统筹规划，小到一个用户故事，大到一个完整的用户特性，都需要考虑怎么合理利用测试资源，所以敏捷项目是非常需要测试策略的。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 1.2em !important;\">具体到实际项目中，通常团队会在项目初期（迭代0）制定测试策略，明确目标(包括功能性需求的目标以及非功能性需求的目标)，然后确定在开发阶段需要添加哪些自动化测试(包括单元测试，接口测试，契约测试，集成测试，系统级别的UI的用户场景测试)，并规定这些测试的大概比率(符合测试金字塔)，选择自动化测试框架（比如XUnit）以及需要哪些手动测试(包括探索性测试，可用性测试等)，还要规划每个发布周期需要进行的测试阶段（比如新功能测试，回归测试等），之后测试策略会对敏捷团队的开发及测试起到非常重要的指导作用，当然，每个团队因为项目的不同策略也会不同。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 1.2em !important;\">下图就是一个简单的敏捷测试策略介绍:</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 1.2em !important;\"><img src=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/aaVJqS7LaMIatF9sGicWb0TnzWwWOLuB6ok6c2KGac3m9ibbR5J0D1QZOzBtH1XaZq6xZ4ykKxuMNcErc2wUPHYg/640?wx_fmt=png&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1\" alt=\"\"/><br/></p><h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 1.3em 0px 1em; font-size: 1.3em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 30px; word-break: break-all; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; color: rgb(78, 161, 219); cursor: pointer; word-break: break-all;\"></a>不需要测试文档</h3><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 1.2em !important;\">测试文档通常包括测试计划，测试用例，测试报告，测试缺陷等文档以及相对应的可以指导测试的一部分需求文档。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 1.2em !important;\">很多人会认为，敏捷软件测试是不需要文档的，敏捷宣言中有一句“工作的软件 高于 详尽的文档”，尽管敏捷宣言最后提到了“右项也有价值，我们更重视左项的价值”，但人们往往会忽视右项的内容，导致在很多刚开始实施敏捷开发的团队中完全否定了测试文档的作用。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 1.2em !important;\">首先不可否认，在实际的敏捷项目中，确实很少见传统意义上的正式的专门的需求文档和测试文档，但这并不代表敏捷项目没有文档，比如用户故事本身就是需求的载体，用户故事中的验收条件就是敏捷测试文档的一部分， 另外很多敏捷软件项目都会采用BDD的方式进行开发，将测试用例用业务人员能够看懂的自然语言描述，并结合自动化实现，形成一个融需求和测试为一体的文档，而且为了应对敏捷软件测试变化快文档更新不及时导致的问题，很多敏捷项目都在使用Living document。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 1.2em !important;\"><img src=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/aaVJqS7LaMIatF9sGicWb0TnzWwWOLuB6qRHozCOFAUiaicTgca4djBjEQMXaBq6EA2sWjCu5ReibibYH6aS7tZN5wQ/640?wx_fmt=png&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1\" alt=\"\"/><br/></p><h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 1.3em 0px 1em; font-size: 1.3em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 30px; word-break: break-all; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; color: rgb(78, 161, 219); cursor: pointer; word-break: break-all;\"></a>纯自动化测试 or 纯手动测试</h3><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 1.2em !important;\">有些刚接触敏捷的人认为敏捷软件开发发布周期很短， 测试人员根本没有时间做手动测试， 所以应该采用纯自动化测试。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 1.2em !important;\">也有一些人认为，敏捷开发强调快速响应变化，如果投入成本在自动化测试上，那么肯定会导致维护自动化测试带来的资源浪费，所以应该采用纯手动测试。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 1.2em !important;\">这是两种极端的误解，虽然这两种观点所考虑到的难点确实存在， 因为在敏捷软件开发过程中， 迭代通常比较短，确实不会预留足够多的时间来做手动测试， 所以必须要有足够多的自动化测试来保障。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 1.2em !important;\">然而因为测试代码本身可能存在缺陷，而且有很多部分难以被自动化测试覆盖(比如界面的测试，可用性测试，探索性测试等)，所以敏捷测试也同样离不开手动测试。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 1.2em !important;\">至于关于自动化测试维护成本的顾虑，敏捷项目也确实存在变化比较多的特点，但通常变的都是比较接近用户的部分，所以应该尽量减少用户级别的依赖界面的自动化测试，而多增加一些不容易变化的底层的单元测试接口测试等。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 1.2em !important;\">推荐敏捷测试以自动化测试为主，手动测试为辅。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 1.2em !important;\"><img src=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/aaVJqS7LaMIatF9sGicWb0TnzWwWOLuB6PTTcIpvdyia4hFtKTt0cM1feianUM73uNoibiaGqZyKvBDFGlwwzvPrtIg/640?wx_fmt=png&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1\" alt=\"\"/><br/></p><h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 1.3em 0px 1em; font-size: 1.3em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 30px; word-break: break-all; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; color: rgb(78, 161, 219); cursor: pointer; word-break: break-all;\"></a>敏捷QA = 敏捷Tester</h3><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 1.2em !important;\">在很多刚接触敏捷实践的团队中，大家对敏捷QA的认识还停留在Tester的阶段，认为只要用户故事开发完成之后，QA去专职地做测试，发现缺陷就够了。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 1.2em !important;\">这是一个很大的误解，首先QA(Quality Assurance/Analyst)，不是单纯意义的测试人员，通过这个角色的名称我们可以看的出来敏捷QA强调的是质量保障和分析，而不单纯是测试产品。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 1.2em !important;\">在实际的项目中，敏捷QA通常会从需求分析阶段就开始参与整个软件开发过程，通过在不同阶段和团队中的不同角色合作，帮助整个团队对质量达成共识，并通过在不同阶段的确认和验证做到缺陷预防，而不是等到软件开发完成后再去发现缺陷，所以对于敏捷QA来说，其目标是软件开发完成后能够发现的缺陷越少越好，而对于Tester来说，发现越多的缺陷证明工作做得越优秀。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 1.2em !important;\"><img src=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/aaVJqS7LaMIatF9sGicWb0TnzWwWOLuB6QyqeIXzezoxwgg0QVhTiat1FFhd2DRiavqy7gWqsTjTTVP5l87WHibjAQ/640?wx_fmt=png&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1\" alt=\"\"/><br/></p><h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 1.3em 0px 1em; font-size: 1.3em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 30px; word-break: break-all; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; color: rgb(78, 161, 219); cursor: pointer; word-break: break-all;\"></a>非功能性测试不重要</h3><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 1.2em !important;\">非功能性测试指的是针对非功能性需求（软件本身满足用户需求所必需的功能性需求以外的一些特性，比如安全，性能，可用性，兼容性等）的测试，通常包括安全测试，性能测试，可用性测试，兼容性测试等。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 1.2em !important;\">在敏捷软件项目中，需求被切割成了很小的单元，在切割的过程中，非功能性需求是最容易被人忽略的一部分，而这导致的问题就是非功能性测试经常被团队忽略，久而久之，就会形成这样一个误解，认为非功能性测试是不重要的。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 1.2em !important;\">这个观点非常不对，首先非功能性测试的重要性并不会因为软件开发模式的不同而有所不同，尤其安全测试和性能测试的重要性正越来越多地被重视起来，因为很多产品必须考虑到用户敏感信息的安全以及性能导致的用户满意度，在敏捷项目中由于软件会尽早发布，如果这些非功能性需求出现问题，就会更早地造成影响，很可能在软件刚步入市场就损失掉大多数的用户。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 1.2em !important;\">所以非功能性的测试和功能性测试同等重要，在实际的项目中，比较好的做法是将这些非功能性需求也加入到用户故事的验收条件中，在整个敏捷开发流程中对这些非功能性需求进行验证。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 1.2em !important;\"><img src=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/aaVJqS7LaMIatF9sGicWb0TnzWwWOLuB6Qr4N7y9w1jxVPojoqBVaf7bic837J4mWgE9ibIw0B2FicELnMfl93AtlA/640?wx_fmt=png&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1\" alt=\"\"/><br/></p><h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 1.3em 0px 1em; font-size: 1.3em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 30px; word-break: break-all; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; color: rgb(78, 161, 219); cursor: pointer; word-break: break-all;\"></a>质量是QA的事儿</h3><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 1.2em !important;\">受传统观念的影响，很多人还是会认为质量是QA的事儿，如果产品发布后质量不好是QA的问题，其他角色和质量没有太大的关系。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 1.2em !important;\">首先这种认识太高估了QA对质量的作用，软件的质量是在软件开发过程中逐步形成的， 从需求分析阶段是否真正的了解到了客户想要的功能，到开发阶段是否增加了足够多的自动化测试保障，是否写了足够健壮的产品代码，到最后测试阶段是否测试了功能引入后整个系统的可用性，不同用户路径是否能正常工作等等，这些都是软件质量的组成部分。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 1.2em !important;\">可以看得出来，在整个过程中，软件的质量离不开敏捷团队各种角色的付出，其中有业务分析人员对需求的准确把握，有开发人员对产品代码的高标准实现，对自动化测试覆盖率的保障，还有QA在整个过程中对质量相关活动的实施和保障，包括需求分析阶段从QA的视角对业务的补充，开发阶段对自动化测试的审查，以及探索性测试可用性测试等对产品质量的进一步保障。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 1.2em !important;\">所以在敏捷测试中更多时候我们会淡化角色的概念，强调团队人人都为质量负责，这样更有助于团队的每一位成员都把质量作为非常重要的一部分，而不是依赖于某个人或者某个角色。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 1.2em !important;\"><img src=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/aaVJqS7LaMIatF9sGicWb0TnzWwWOLuB6H6Qboic5Ia0201BOyDTPULGV3CGWGdic362X2K6Jfd2KnYYAib4mOiaGfg/640?wx_fmt=png&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1\" alt=\"\"/><br/></p><h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 1.3em 0px 1em; font-size: 1.3em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 30px; word-break: break-all; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; color: rgb(78, 161, 219); cursor: pointer; word-break: break-all;\"></a>开发可以写测试，不再需要QA了</h3><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 1.2em !important;\">因为敏捷团队强调人人都为质量负责，开发人员会采用TDD等方式写大量的自动化测试，那么是不是就不需要QA了？</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 1.2em !important;\">对于这个观点，在社区有过很多激烈的讨论，比如这篇文章《我们需要专职的QA吗？》就曾经引起了很大的争议，其实个人认为这篇文章里提到的QA指的是Tester，具体两者的区别可参考前面的观点；抛开这个，作者的某些观点其实是很有价值的，比如作者最后提到了质量不是测出来的，要通过软件生命周期各个阶段相关活动的保障，而这些活动都离不开QA的参与。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 1.2em !important;\">首先需求分析阶段，QA可以从不同的视角对于需求提出疑问，补充，修改，因为QA特有的技术背景，对于软件的可用性等有更深入的理解，所以往往可以提出不同于业务分析师和开发人员的观点；开发阶段，QA也会审查开发人员写的自动化测试，通过QA的专业测试背景帮助开发人员写更有价值的测试，比如我们在项目中曾经发现开发人员写了很多没有业务价值的测试；测试阶段，探索性测试，可用性测试，安全测试，性能测试等都是QA们在做的事情。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 1.2em !important;\">当然，如果业务分析师从各种视角把业务分析的透彻完美，开发人员可以写非常有价值的测试，也可以做各种类型的手动测试，那么去掉专职QA也不是不可以，那样的话不是不需要QA，而是人人都是QA。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 1.2em !important;\"><img src=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/aaVJqS7LaMIatF9sGicWb0TnzWwWOLuB6HpAQPZPwk45iab9PT95SLpkv9vvS71Oks3AN7qzY8zfhXJetIHicse2g/640?wx_fmt=png&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1\" alt=\"\"/><br/></p><h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 1.3em 0px 1em; font-size: 1.3em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 30px; word-break: break-all; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; color: rgb(78, 161, 219); cursor: pointer; word-break: break-all;\"></a>结论</h3><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 1.2em !important;\">以上列出来的七点是刚刚接触敏捷测试时很容易进入的误区，甚至有的观点在一些已经施行敏捷很长时间的团队中仍然存在，这些观点很容易导致敏捷测试走上弯路，以上是结合实际项目经验个人的一些思考，希望对大家有所帮助。</p><p><br/></p>', '2018-06-09 18:26:13', '2018-06-09 18:26:13', '1', '2', '1', '0');
INSERT INTO `forum` VALUES ('19', '想转行人工智能？机会来了！！！', '<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">梯度方向直方图&nbsp;<br/>原文路径：<a href=\"https://www.learnopencv.com/histogram-of-oriented-gradients/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(103, 149, 181); text-decoration-line: none; outline: 0px; cursor: pointer; word-break: break-all;\">https://www.learnopencv.com/histogram-of-oriented-gradients/</a></p><h2 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; font-weight: 500; line-height: 32px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); margin: 8px 0px 16px; font-size: 24px; white-space: normal; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(78, 161, 219); outline: 0px; cursor: pointer; word-break: break-all;\"></a>最近在搞车牌识别的时候，训练样本去识别车牌的时候用到HOG特征。国外一篇文章让我受益良多</h2><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">什么是特征描述符？&nbsp;<br/>特征描述符是指通过提取有用的信息并抛弃无关的信息来表示这一张图片或者一张图片的一部分</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">典型地，特征描述符将大小宽度x高度x 3（通道）的图像转换为特征向量数组，长度n。例如：在HOG特征描述器的情况下，输入图像大小为64×128×3，输出特征向量长度为3780。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">【&nbsp;<br/>中间有一个循环装箱的过程&nbsp;<br/>划分为8x8大小的图像补丁块处理，装到9个箱子（其中8x8、9 这些参数都是不固定的，但是是推荐的）&nbsp;<br/>移动步伐：8个像素&nbsp;<br/>width:64 /8 == 8 份&nbsp;<br/>Height:128 /8 ==16份&nbsp;<br/>用一个16x16的窗口来处理，可以包含4个8X8的图像补丁，那么处理一次会有得到4*9个箱子数据。循环处理&nbsp;<br/>最后能循环 7*15=105次&nbsp;<br/>105*36=3780个箱子数据，存储的是每个像素的梯度大小和梯度方向&nbsp;<br/>】</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">记住，HOG特征描述符能够用其他的尺寸大小来计算，但是在下面的具体例子里为了让你更加容易理解相关概念，选择使用图像宽高：64×128，图像补丁 8x8 窗口 16X16 移动步长 8个像素</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">首先来了解什么是“有用的信息”、什么是“无关的信息”？我们需要明确知道“有用”是指对什么有用。&nbsp;<br/>特征向量对查看图像是没有用的，但是，对于图像识别和目标检测这些任务是非常有用的。将这些算法生成的特征向量引入到支持向量机（SVM）等图像分类算法中，可以取得不错的效果。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">但是，哪一种“特征”对分类任务才是真正有用的呢？让我们用一个例子来讨论这一点。 假设我们要建立一个物体检测仪，用来检测衬衫和大衣的纽扣。按钮是圆形的（在图像中可能看起来是椭圆的），通常有几个洞用于缝纫。 你可以在一个按钮的图像上运行一个边缘检测器，只需简单地观察边缘图像就可以很容易地判断它是否是一个按钮。在这种情况下，边缘信息是“有用的”，而颜色信息不是。 此外，该功能还需要有鉴别能力。例如，从图像中提取的良好特征应该能够分辨按钮和其他圆形物体，如硬币和汽车轮胎的区别。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">在HOG特征描述器中，梯度方向（梯度）的分布（直方图）作为特征。 图像的梯度（x和y导数）是有用的，因为梯度的大小在边缘和拐角处（突然强度变化的区域）很大，而且我们知道边和角在物体形状上的信息比平面区域要多得多。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">怎么去计算方向梯度直方图？&nbsp;<br/>在这一节中，我们将深入研究计算HOG特征描述符的细节。为了说明每一步，我们将使用一个图像块。</p><h2 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; font-weight: 500; line-height: 32px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); margin: 8px 0px 16px; font-size: 24px; white-space: normal; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(78, 161, 219); outline: 0px; cursor: pointer; word-break: break-all;\"></a>步骤1：预处理</h2><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">如前所述的HOG特征描述符用于行人检测，是在64×128片图像计算。当然，图像可能是任意大小的。通常在多个尺度上分析多个图像位置，唯一的限制是被分析的补丁具有固定的长宽比（纵横比）。在我们的例子中，补丁需要有一个长宽比为1:2。例如，他们可以100×200, 128×256，或1000×2000而不是101×205。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">为了说明这一点，下面展示了一个大尺寸的720×475图像。我们计算我们的HOG特征描述符选择一块大小100×200。这个补丁被裁剪的图像并调整其大小以64×128。现在已经准备好计算这个图像补丁的HOG描述符了。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img title=\"\" alt=\"这里写图片描述\" src=\"http://localhost:8080/ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20180609/1528539716567059451.png\"/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">还有一个预处理步骤就是“伽玛校正”，但性能提升非常小，所以这里跳过该步骤。</p><h2 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; font-weight: 500; line-height: 32px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); margin: 8px 0px 16px; font-size: 24px; white-space: normal; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(78, 161, 219); outline: 0px; cursor: pointer; word-break: break-all;\"></a>步骤2：计算图像梯度</h2><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">要计算一个HOG描述符，我们首先需要计算水平和垂直梯度；毕竟，我们要计算梯度直方图。通过用以下内核过滤图像很容易做到这一点。&nbsp;<br/><img title=\"\" alt=\"这里写图片描述\" src=\"http://localhost:8080/ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20180609/1528539717083093918.png\"/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">我们可以在opencv中使用内核大小为1的Sobel算子实现同样的结果。</p><pre class=\"prettyprint\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; overflow-x: auto; overflow-y: hidden; font-family: Consolas, Inconsolata, Courier, monospace; font-size: 14px; padding: 8px 16px 4px 56px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 24px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; background-color: rgb(246, 248, 250); border: none; border-radius: 4px; outline: 0px; position: relative;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;//&nbsp;Read&nbsp;image\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Mat&nbsp;img&nbsp;=&nbsp;imread(&quot;F:/data/car/test1.jpg&quot;);\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;img.convertTo(img,&nbsp;CV_32F,&nbsp;1&nbsp;/&nbsp;255.0);&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;//&nbsp;Calculate&nbsp;gradients&nbsp;gx,&nbsp;gy\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Mat&nbsp;gx,&nbsp;gy;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;//对X梯度绝对值\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Sobel(img,&nbsp;gx,&nbsp;CV_32F,&nbsp;1,&nbsp;0,&nbsp;1);&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;//对Y梯度绝对值\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Sobel(img,&nbsp;gy,&nbsp;CV_32F,&nbsp;0,&nbsp;1,&nbsp;1);12345678910</pre><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">接下来，我们可以用下面的公式找到梯度的大小和方向</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img title=\"\" alt=\"这里写图片描述\" src=\"http://localhost:8080/ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20180609/1528539717638049398.png\"/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">如果你是使用opencv，计算梯度的大小和方向可以使用函数carttopolar，如下所示。</p><pre class=\"prettyprint\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; overflow-x: auto; overflow-y: hidden; font-family: Consolas, Inconsolata, Courier, monospace; font-size: 14px; padding: 8px 16px 4px 56px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 24px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; background-color: rgb(246, 248, 250); border: none; border-radius: 4px; outline: 0px; position: relative;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Mat&nbsp;mag,&nbsp;angle;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;//mag&nbsp;坡度梯度&nbsp;大小\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;//mag就是大小&nbsp;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;//angle就是方向\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;cartToPolar(gx,&nbsp;gy,&nbsp;mag,&nbsp;angle,&nbsp;1);12345</pre><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">下图显示了梯度</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img title=\"\" alt=\"这里写图片描述\" src=\"http://localhost:8080/ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20180609/1528539718091060419.png\"/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">注意，图x梯度在垂直线方向延伸，图y-梯度在水平线方向延伸。图坡度梯度在强度上有急剧的变化。当图片区域光滑时，都没有延伸。我故意遗漏了显示渐变方向的图像，因为作为图像显示的方向不能传达太多信息。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">注意看图像的变化&nbsp;<br/>渐变图像去除了许多非必要的信息（例如恒定的彩色背景），但突出显示了轮廓。换句话说，你可以看到渐变图像，并且很容易地辨别出图片中有一个人。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">图x梯度 注意水平方向基本没有延伸&nbsp;<br/>图y梯度 注意垂直方向基本没有延伸</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img title=\"\" alt=\"这里写图片描述\" src=\"http://localhost:8080/ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20180609/1528539719148043161.png\"/></p><h2 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; font-weight: 500; line-height: 32px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); margin: 8px 0px 16px; font-size: 24px; white-space: normal; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(78, 161, 219); outline: 0px; cursor: pointer; word-break: break-all;\"></a>步骤3：计算在8×8细胞梯度直方图</h2><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">在这一步中，图像被分为8×8细胞和梯度直方图计算每个8×8细胞。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img title=\"\" alt=\"这里写图片描述\" src=\"http://localhost:8080/ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20180609/1528539720044095894.png\"/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">我们将学习了解在一瞬间的直方图，但是在我们去之前就让我们先了解为什么我们把图像分为8×8细胞。使用特征描述符描述图像补丁的一个重要原因是它提供了一个紧凑的表示。8×8图像补丁包含8x8x3 = 192像素值。这个补丁梯度每像素包含2个值（大小和方向），那就变成8x8x2 = 128个数。通过这一部分的最后我们会看到这128个数字是用9-bin直方图(可存储为长度9的数组，通俗地说是分别装到9个箱子里)表示。不仅是表示更简洁，计算在补丁直方图具有更强的健壮性。个别的颜色梯度可能有噪音，但用一个8x8图像补丁来表示梯度直方图对噪声不敏感，换句话说，就是受噪音影响不大。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">但是什么是8x8图像补丁？为什么不是32x32？这是我们通过特征缩放来寻找到的明确的选择。HOG最初用于检测行人。在一张行人照片缩放到64×128，使用8×8细胞足以捕捉有趣的功能（如面部、头部的等）。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">让我们看一个8×8补丁在图像梯度的面貌</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img title=\"\" alt=\"这里写图片描述\" src=\"http://localhost:8080/ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20180609/1528539720432074226.png\"/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">中间的图像信息量是非常大的。它显示了用箭头表示梯度的图像的贴片，箭头显示梯度的方向，其长度显示大小。注意箭头的方向如何指向强度的变化方向，其大小表示差异的大小。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">在右边，我们看到原始的数字表示在8×8细胞有一个小的差异，那就是角度是0度和180度的梯度，而不是0到360度之间。这些被称为“无符号”渐变，因为梯度正值和它的负值用相同的数字表示。换句话说，梯度箭头和与之相对的180度箭头被认为是相同的。但是，为什么不使用0 - 360度呢？经验表明，无符号梯度比签名梯度更好地用于行人检测。HOG的一些实现将允许您指定是否使用带符号的渐变。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">下一步是创建一个8×8细胞梯度直方图。直方图包含9个箱子对应角度0, 20, 40…160。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">下图说明了这个过程。我们正在前面的图寻找在同8×8补丁梯度的幅值和方向。根据方向选择箱子，并根据大小选择投票（进入箱子的值）。让我们首先关注环绕在蓝色中的像素。它的角度（方向）为80度，大小为2。所以它放入到第五个箱子。用红色包围的像素的梯度方向为10度，大小为4。由于10度是0和20之间的一半，所以像素的也是均匀地分成两个箱子。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img title=\"\" alt=\"这里写图片描述\" src=\"http://localhost:8080/ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20180609/1528539721068003912.png\"/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">还有一个细节需要注意。如果角度大于160度，则在160到180之间，我们知道角度绕成0和180相等。因此，在下面的例子中，角度为165度的像素正比于0度的箱子和160度的箱子。&nbsp;<br/>从160-180&nbsp;<br/>180-165/165-160=3&nbsp;<br/>所以0箱子分4/1，160箱子分4/3</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">在8×8细胞中所有像素的贡献加起来创造9-bin直方图。对于上面的补丁，它看起来像这样</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img title=\"\" alt=\"这里写图片描述\" src=\"http://localhost:8080/ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20180609/1528539721324075018.png\"/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">在我们的表示中，y轴是0度。你可以看到直方图在0度和180度附近占很大比重。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img title=\"\" alt=\"这里写图片描述\" src=\"http://localhost:8080/ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20180609/1528539721708032880.png\"/></p><h2 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; font-weight: 500; line-height: 32px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); margin: 8px 0px 16px; font-size: 24px; white-space: normal; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(78, 161, 219); outline: 0px; cursor: pointer; word-break: break-all;\"></a>步骤4：16x16步块归一化</h2><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">在前面的步骤中，我们根据图像的梯度创建了一个直方图。图像的梯度对整体亮度是敏感的。如果通过将所有像素值除以2来使图像变暗，则渐变幅度将改变一半，因此直方图值将改变一半。理想情况下，我们希望描述符不受光照变化的影响。换句话说，我们希望使直方图正常化(归一化)，这样它们不会受到光照变化的影响。&nbsp;<br/>在解释直方图是如何规范化之前，让我们看看长度为3的向量是如何规范化的。&nbsp;<br/><img title=\"\" alt=\"这里写图片描述\" src=\"http://localhost:8080/ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20180609/1528539722029030538.png\"/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">例如：一个像素向量RGB【128,64,32】，向量的长度则为：sqrt{128^2 + 64^2 + 32^2} = 146.64&nbsp;<br/>这也被称为向量的L2范数。将向量的每一个元素除以146.64得到归一化向量【0.87,0.43,0.22】，可以看到，归一化后的【256,128,32】将得到【0.87,0.43,0.22】可以看到归一化向量消除了规模。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">现在我们知道了如何归一化一个矢量，你可能会认为在计算HOG特征时可以将9x1的直方图以上述的3×1矢量的方式归一化。可以是可以，但更好的办法是归一化一个更大尺寸的16×16块。16×16块用4个直方图可级联成一个36×1元矢量，使用3×1矢量归一化的方法。然后通过8像素的窗口移动（见动画）重复计算，归一化的36×1向量。</p><h2 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; font-weight: 500; line-height: 32px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); margin: 8px 0px 16px; font-size: 24px; white-space: normal; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(78, 161, 219); outline: 0px; cursor: pointer; word-break: break-all;\"></a>步骤5：计算HOG特征向量</h2><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">计算整个图像补丁最终的特征向量，36×1载体连接成一个巨大的载体。这个向量的大小是多少？&nbsp;<br/>原图截取100*200—&gt;resize—&gt;64*128&nbsp;<br/>64/8=8&nbsp;<br/>128/8=16&nbsp;<br/>1、我们有多少个16×16块吗？有7个水平和15个垂直位置，总共7×15＝105个块。&nbsp;<br/>2、每16×16块由36×1矢量表示。所以当我们连接成一个巨大的载体，他们都得到了36×105 = 3780维向量。</p><h2 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; font-weight: 500; line-height: 32px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); margin: 8px 0px 16px; font-size: 24px; white-space: normal; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(78, 161, 219); outline: 0px; cursor: pointer; word-break: break-all;\"></a>定向梯度直方图的可视化</h2><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img title=\"这里写图片描述\" alt=\"这里写图片描述\" src=\"http://localhost:8080/ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20180609/1528539722363084867.png\" width=\"378\" height=\"661\"/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">一个图像块的HOG特征描述符通常是通过在8×8组织的9×1归一化直方图可视化。见上图像。你会注意到，直方图的主导方向捕捉人的形状，特别是围绕躯干和腿。&nbsp;<br/>不幸的是，没有简单的方法来可视化OpenCV的HOG描述符。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">至此：翻译完成，英语水平有限，有错误的地方，希望不吝赐教。</p><p><br/></p>', '2018-06-09 18:27:27', '2018-06-09 18:27:27', '1', '2', '0', '0');
INSERT INTO `forum` VALUES ('20', '九年铸剑 这家公司开启SaaS全面定制时代', '<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px 8px 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; font-size: 15px;\">SaaS要实现全面定制难不难？<br/></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px 8px 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; font-size: 15px;\">难！因为每一家企业的业务都存在差异化。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px 8px 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; font-size: 15px;\">但也不难！因为有一家云计算公司已开启了SaaS全面定制之路。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px 8px 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; font-size: 15px;\">众所周知，SaaS市场近年来发展迅速，受到越来越多用户的欢迎，但SaaS面临的终极挑战即：针对企业核心业务的深度定制与人力成本、规模化的不可兼得。近日，搭搭云宣布搭搭云3.0平台正式上线，该平台是集微信、网站、APP和企业软件一体化的企业管理“超级应用”平台，为中小微企业提供全面移动化、系统平台化、业务一体化、定制个性化的SaaS服务，宣告了SaaS全面定制时代的到来。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px 8px 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; font-size: 15px;\">为什么是搭搭云率先开启SaaS全面定制时代？这还得从“一个疯狂的想法”说起。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px 8px 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; font-size: 15px;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px 8px 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; font-size: 15px;\"></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: center; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px 8px 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; font-size: 15px;\"></span><br/></p><p><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: center; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(0, 128, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; font-weight: 700; word-break: break-all;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; text-align: justify;\">“一个疯狂的想法”</span></span></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px 8px 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; font-size: 15px;\">作为中国第一代电子商务的拓荒者，搭搭云创始人万斌在多个行业积累了多年的技术和行业经验。2007年，在跑遍全球超过500家企业之后，万斌亲眼见证了国内企业和国外企业在数字化管理手段、方法的巨大差距，数字化管理方法的落后使得国内企业在成本和效率上远远落后，于是他诞生出一个疯狂的想法：研发一款软件，功能全面，不按照模块划分，数据天然互通，并且是在线动态可修改的，在线交付和在线使用。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px 8px 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; font-size: 15px;\">“当时业界朋友听到我的想法之后，都说这是一个疯狂的想法。”万斌表示道。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px 8px 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; font-size: 15px;\">经过两年的软件框架设计，2009年搭搭云的前身九章信息科技公司正式成立。此后九年里，搭搭云陆续推出两个版本的产品，直到现在搭搭云3.0平台的上线，当初那个“疯狂的想法”得以实现。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px 8px 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; font-size: 15px;\">万斌表示：“九年磨一剑，中间充满了曲折和艰辛，搭搭云3.0平台真正让用户远离过去碎片化的采购，实现了软件开发周期的大幅缩短、成本的大幅降低。”</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px 8px 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; font-size: 15px;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px 8px 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; font-size: 15px;\"></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: center; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px 8px 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; font-size: 15px;\"></span><br/></p><p><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: center; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(0, 128, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; font-weight: 700; word-break: break-all;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; text-align: justify;\">搭搭云3.0超级应用平台有何奇妙之处？</span></span></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px 8px 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; font-size: 15px;\">在“大众创新、万众创业”的热潮带动下，中国的中小微企业呈现出喷薄而发的状态，成为市场中最活跃的一股力量。不可否认的是，中小微企业也存在着业务变化快，通常是计划赶不上变化，外加上预算有限，中小微企业对于软件的定制化需求更加实时化、灵活化和个性化，标准化的SaaS产品已经很难满足这种需求趋势。正所谓天下武功唯快不破，在搭搭云看来，“快速定制”和“快速修改”会是未来用户在SaaS市场选择的第一标准。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px 8px 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; font-size: 15px;\">目前，SaaS的全面定制化已经成为所有SaaS云计算公司努力的方向，在万斌看来，不同SaaS公司所瞄准的痛点和方案不同，搭搭云瞄准的是中小微企业个性化定制方面的痛点，“企业的核心业务都是个性化的，但是现在SaaS主要问题包括，一是功能单一、不够全面；二是个性化能力不够，软件不适合用户；三是软件不能适应用户业务快速变化；四是移动化。”</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px 8px 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; font-size: 15px;\">为此，搭搭云3.0平台实现了集成微信、网站、APP和企业软件一体化，用户在一个云端账户内就可做到企业的全方位管理，定制和使用各种企业应用，并可以在线实时调整、即改即用、移动端免开发实时同步。搭搭云创始人万斌表示：“80%的功能调整可以在1小时内完成，并且可以马上投入使用，移动端也可以实现同步使用。这种快速、灵活的特性正是广大中小微企业所渴望的。”</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px 8px 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; font-size: 15px;\">根据介绍，搭搭云3.0超级应用平台拥有全面个性化定制能力，所有应用都可以通过零代码或低代码方式进行全面定制，绝非简单的模块拼接；并能够实现全面移动化，移动端面开发，应用功能和数据在PC和移动端实时同步，原生动态，大幅降低定制的技术门槛和开放按成本；同时，平台一个账号集成了多种企业管理软件，能满足复杂业务需求，数据天然互通，杜绝了信息孤岛；在线实时修改、交付、使用则为用户提供了高度的灵活性。“搭搭云3.0采用了人工智能技术和自然语言交互技术，通过超级应用方式，大幅降低了技术门槛，让业务人员和管理人员都可以加入到软件创造之中。”万斌表示。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px 8px 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; font-size: 15px;\">“采用零代码或者低代码的方式开发软件已经成为趋势，中国未来也会是这样，软件开发人员未来的工作重点将会转移到业务逻辑之上。”万斌补充道。而知名技术专家赫华也认为低代码开发平台对企业的数字化转型帮助巨大，在她看来，低代码开发平台这种方式有三大好处：“第一，企业可以自主、独立和快速开发个性化应用；第二，开发模式发生改变，开发人员重点是配置功能，考虑业务流程和业务价值去开发应用；第三，快速应对数字化快速的节奏，让企业创新的想法得以落地，获得市场竞争力。”</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px 8px 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; font-size: 15px;\">据悉，搭搭云超级应用该平台已经在超过30个行业的2000多家企业得到了验证，获得了大量用户的广泛认可。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px 8px 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; font-size: 15px;\">银川新华百货商业集团股份有限公司副总裁剡玉香表示，公司主营家用电器和手机，拥有员工1300多人，200多种岗位，下辖商铺90多家，业务、组织架构复杂，利用搭搭云平台构建了工作计划管理、人事手续管理、人力资源管理、组织结构管理四大企业管理“神器”，大幅提升了管理效率，简化工作流程。“业务人员自己就可以上手操作和搭建管理模型、工具，非常快捷、简单和使用。”</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px 8px 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; font-size: 15px;\">诸如银川新百的客户还有很多，它们都受益于搭搭云超级应用平台的个性化定制，降低了软件创作、交付、使用的门槛。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px 8px 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; font-size: 15px;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px 8px 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; font-size: 15px;\"></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: center; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px 8px 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; font-size: 15px;\"></span><br/></p><p><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: center; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; font-weight: 700; word-break: break-all;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; text-align: justify; color: rgb(0, 128, 255);\">搭搭云携手合作伙伴重塑渠道价值</span></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px 8px 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; font-size: 15px;\">随着搭搭云3.0平台发布，搭搭云还推出了生态建设计划，希望通过生态的力量，让合作伙伴和用户都享受到超级应用平台带来的好处。对于一家SaaS云计算公司而言，用户通常可以直接在其平台上购买产品和服务，为什么搭搭云仍然会力推渠道合作伙伴计划呢？</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px 8px 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; font-size: 15px;\">万斌表示：“SaaS的核心价值在于服务，而渠道商的核心价值就是服务。搭搭云的客户触及能力是有限的，需要广大合作伙伴一起推动SaaS全面定制化。渠道商拥有最后一公里的服务能力，这是无法替代的。SaaS提供直接购买的方式和产品功能单一的方式其实是给渠道商带来了很大的冲击，渠道商是一群真正提供服务的群体，”</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px 8px 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; font-size: 15px;\">当前，几乎所有软件公司都采用“平台+二次开发”的模式进行渠道拓展，渠道商具有一定实施能力之后，可为用户提供一定的个性化定制能力，但是定制范围不会超过平台本身的框架。搭搭云首席运营官王庆飞表示：“企业对SaaS的需求正在快速变化，功能全面、快速灵活、个性化是最突出的需求；因此，渠道商也应该重塑价值，来积极应对这种变化，必须改变过去单一软件功能、开发周期长、成本高、交付难的情况。搭搭云有着弱技术化的特点，渠道商与搭搭云合作有着巨大的价值，搭搭云处于生态系统的底部，负责搭搭云平台的升级和维护，基于搭搭云独有的智能和动态化技术，渠道商可以从零开始搭建自己的应用产品，可以是OA、CRM、HR，也可以是财务、进销存或者ERP，渠道商的多年行业沉淀和服务能力会得到充分展现。”</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px 8px 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; font-size: 15px;\">根据搭搭云介绍，生态化战略推出之后，搭搭云将不会为终端企业直接提供任何应用层面的服务，让行业渠道商充分发挥服务价值。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px 8px 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; font-size: 15px;\"></span><br/></p><p><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: center; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; font-weight: 700; word-break: break-all;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; text-align: justify; color: rgb(0, 128, 255);\">未来：向智能化迈进</span></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px 8px 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; font-size: 15px;\">成立九年来，搭搭云最近刚完成了千万级人民币的A轮融资，随着生态化战略的实施，搭搭云的布局逐步完善。万斌表示，经过9年的历练，搭搭云的产品、技术以及商业模式都得到了广大用户的验证，公司接下来将投入更多资源来实现扩张，接下来将重点考虑三个方面：</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px 8px 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; font-size: 15px;\">首先，将持续加大对研发的投入，更大规模的引入人工智能技术和自然语言交互技术，提升SaaS产品的智能化程度；</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px 8px 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; font-size: 15px;\">第二，会吸引更多行业专家和合作伙伴加入搭搭云；</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px 8px 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; font-size: 15px;\">第三，与业界各种力量一起推动SaaS全面定制化；</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: 