 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; font-size: 15px;\">这分别是单人、双人、四人模式下，玩家每场比赛的击杀人数图，可以看到不管是在哪种模式下，能够完成7击杀以上的人都是非常非常少的。<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; font-weight: 700; word-break: break-all;\">击杀人数大多数分布在0人和1人，能够完成2人击杀已经很了不起了。小E这才平静了下来。</span></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 1.5em; text-align: center; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(166, 91, 203);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; font-weight: 700; word-break: break-all;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; font-size: 15px;\">三、是该单打独斗还是跟队友一起配合？</span></span></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 1.5em; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; font-size: 15px;\">有些人放荡不羁爱自由（基友），比如说我，在经历了一次出门舔箱被猪队友打成筛子之后，总是愿意在四人模式下也自己单干。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 1.5em; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; font-size: 15px;\">但是，跟队友打配合和助攻，是不是更容易吃鸡呢？</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 1.5em; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; font-size: 15px;\">看图：</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 1.5em; text-align: center; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 1.5em; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; font-weight: 700; word-break: break-all;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; font-size: 15px;\">发现助攻次数跟吃鸡概率也是成正比关系的，5次助攻吃鸡概率为50%，助攻11次以上锁定吃鸡。</span></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 1.5em; text-align: center; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(166, 91, 203);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; font-weight: 700; word-break: break-all;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; font-size: 15px;\">四、“毒来了我跑不过毒怎么办”之车辆到底有多重要</span></span></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 1.5em; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; font-size: 15px;\">其实，在后面的死因分析中发现，玩家死于Bluezone也是一个很高的死因，也就是被毒死了。纯靠跑很多时候是跑不过毒的。Alfred也曾有过身上携带着好多个急救包一边跑一边急救（手动苦笑）最后还是倒在了路上的状况。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 1.5em; text-align: center; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 1.5em; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; font-size: 15px;\">所以，有车一族真的可以很帅气！看上图，没有搭乘过车辆的吃鸡概率是0.007，而搭乘过车辆的吃鸡概率是0.058。也就是说，<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; font-weight: 700; word-break: break-all;\">有车可以把吃鸡概率提高8倍！</span></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 1.5em; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; font-weight: 700; word-break: break-all;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; font-size: 15px;\">下回跟队友打的时候，必须得有一个人专门去找车。</span></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 1.5em; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; font-size: 15px;\">再来看一张图：</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 1.5em; text-align: center; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 1.5em; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-famil