<br/></span></h2><h2 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.75em; word-break: break-all; white-space: normal; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; color: rgb(78, 161, 219); cursor: pointer; word-break: break-all;\"></a><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(255, 129, 36);\">基于多机多卡的大数据声学模型训练</span></span></h2><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 17px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; white-space: normal; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 17px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; white-space: normal; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\">实际的语音识别服务通常会面对非常复杂的语音数据，语音识别声学模型一定要尽可能地覆盖各种可能的场景，包括各种对话、各种声道、各种噪音甚至各种口音，这就意味着海量的数据。而如何应用海量数据快速训练声学模型并上线服务，就直接关系到业务相应速度。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 17px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; white-space: normal; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 17px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; white-space: normal; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\">我们利用阿里的Max-Compute计算平台和多机多卡并行训练工具，在使用8机16GPU卡、训练数据为5000小时的情况下，关于LFR-DFSMN声学模型和LFR-LCBLSTM的训练速度如下表：</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 17px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; white-space: normal; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\"><br/></span></p><table width=\"852\" style=\"width: 707px;\"><tbody style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; border: 0px; word-break: break-all; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><tr style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; border-width: 1px 0px 0px; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: initial; border-left-style: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: initial; border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; border-top-style: solid; border-top-color: rgb(221, 221, 221); word-break: break-all; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\" class=\"firstRow\"><td width=\"192\" valign=\"top\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px 7px; margin: 0px; text-align: left; word-break: break-all; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 22px;\"><br/></td><td width=\"204\" valign=\"top\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px 7px; margin: 0px; text-align: left; word-break: break-all; border-left: none; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 22px;\"><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; line-height: 1.75em; word-break: break-all; clear: both; min-height: 1em;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\">处理一个epoch需要的时间</span></p></td></tr><tr style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; border-widt