m-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 12px;\">3.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Zhang S, Liu C, Jiang H, et al. Feedforwardsequential memory networks: A new structure to learn long-term dependency[J].arXiv preprint arXiv:1512.08301, 2015.</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 17px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 1.75em; word-break: break-all; white-space: normal; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 12px;\">4.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Zhang S, Jiang H, Xiong S, et al. CompactFeedforward Sequential Memory Networks for Large Vocabulary Continuous SpeechRecognition[C]//INTERSPEECH. 2016: 3389-3393.</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 17px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 1.75em; word-break: break-all; white-space: normal; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box