an></p></li><li><p><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; color: black; background-color: inherit;\">logreg&nbsp;=&nbsp;linear_model.LogisticRegression(C=<span class=\"number\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; background-color: inherit;\">1e5</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; background-color: inherit;\">)&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></p></li><li><p><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; color: black; background-color: inherit;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p></li><li><p><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; color: black; background-color: inherit;\">a&nbsp;=&nbsp;logreg.fit(X,&nbsp;Y)&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p></li><li><p><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; color: black; background-color: inherit;\">a.coef_&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"comment\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; color: rgb(0, 130, 0); background-color: inherit;\">#返回参数的系数</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; background-color: inherit;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></p></li><li><p><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; color: black; background-color: inherit;\">a.predict(X)&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"comment\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; color: rgb(0, 130, 0); background-color: inherit;\">#预测类别</span><span style=\"box-siz