lor: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Arial, Tahoma, Helvetica, 宋体;\">12、导引线　　</span><br/><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Arial, Tahoma, Helvetica, 宋体;\">13、编码工具条　</span><br/><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Arial, Tahoma, Helvetica, 宋体;\">14、代码折叠　</span><br/><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Arial, Tahoma, Helvetica, 宋体;\">15、文件比较功能　</span><br/><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Arial, Tahoma, Helvetica, 宋体;\">16、编码功能改进　</span><br/><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Arial, Tahoma, Helvetica, 宋体;\">17、支持WebDAV</span><br/><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Arial, Tahoma, Helvetica, 宋体;\">18、插入Flash视频</span></p><p class=\"itTit\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 2px 8px; margin-top: 6px; margin-bottom: 6px; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(0, 153, 51); font-weight: bold; line-height: 24px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; white-space: normal; background: rgb(246, 246, 246); border: 1px solid rgb(238, 238, 238); font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, 微软雅黑, 宋体;\">绿色版使用说明：</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: bre