line: 0px; padding-bottom: 15px; line-height: 22px; word-break: break-all;\">14</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding-bottom: 15px; line-height: 22px; word-break: break-all;\">15</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding-bottom: 15px; line-height: 22px; word-break: break-all;\">16</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding-bottom: 15px; line-height: 22px; word-break: break-all;\">17</p></td><td style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px 6px; margin: 0px; word-break: break-all; border-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 22px;\"><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding-bottom: 15px; line-height: 22px; word-break: break-all;\">function a () {</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding-bottom: 15px; line-height: 22px; word-break: break-all;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;b();</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding-bottom: 15px; line-height: 22px; word-break: break-all;\">}</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding-bottom: 15px; line-height: 22px; word-break: break-all;\">function b() {</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding-bottom: 15px; line-height: 22px; word-break: break-all;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;c();&nbsp;</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding-bottom: 15px; line-height: 22px; word-break: break-all;\">}</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding-bottom: 15px; line-height: 22px; word-break: break-all;\">function c() {</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding-bottom: 15px; line-height: 22px; word-break: break-all;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;//在该处断点,查看call stack&nbsp;</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding-bottom: 15px; line-height: 22px; word-break: break-all;\">}</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding-bottom: 15px; line-height: 22px; word-break: break-all;\">a-&gt;b-&gt;c.</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding-bottom: 15px; line-height: 22px; word-break: break-all;\">call stack 从上到下的顺序就是</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding-bottom: 15px; line-height: 22px; word-break: break-all;\">c</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding-bottom: 15px; line-height: 22px; word-break: break-all;\">b</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding-bottom: 15px; line-height: 22px; word-break: break-all;\">a</p></td></tr></tbody></table><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 15px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;\">2、在区域2中你的断点调试信息。当某个断点在执行的时候对应的信息会高亮,双击该处信息可以在区域2中快速定位。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 15px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;\">3、添加的Dom监控信息。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 15px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;\">4、击+ 并输入 URL 包含的字符串即可监听该 URL 的 Ajax 请求,输入内容就相当于 URL 的过滤器。如果什么都不填,那么就监听所有 XHR 请求。一旦 XHR 调用触发时就会在 request.send() 的地方中断。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 15px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;\">5、为网页添加各种类型的断点信息。如选中了Mouse中的某一项(click),当你在网页上出发这个动作(单击网页任意地方),你浏览器就是立刻断点监控该事件。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 15px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;\">值得再次重复一遍,Sources是一般的功能开发中最常用到也是最有用的功能面板,它里面的许多功能对于我们开发前端工程来说是非常有帮助的。在web2.0时代的今天,我不推荐依然在自己的代码里面写调试信息的行为,因为这会然你的开发变得繁琐。Chrome开发工具给我们提供的强大功能,我们应该好好利用之。这篇文章就到此结束,虽然有点繁琐,但总算基本表述了卤煮使用经验和想法,希望对你有帮助。如果你觉得不错,请推荐一下本文并继续关注卤煮在的博客。在下一篇中我将向大家介绍Chrome开发工具中的性能方面的调试。</p><p><br/></p>', '2018-06-09 19:21:19', '2018-06-09 19:21:19', '1', '4', '3', '0');
INSERT INTO `forum` VALUES ('37', 'jqgrid的函数与操作', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">jqGrid有两种调用方式：</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 30px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(153, 51, 102);\">$(&quot;#grid_id&quot;).jqGridMethod( parameter1,...,parameterN );</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: Arial;\">或</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 30px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(153, 51, 102);\">$(&quot;#grid_id&quot;).jqGrid(&#39;method&#39;, parameter1,...,parameterN );</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 30px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: Arial;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: Arial;\">首先介绍一下jqGrid的几个最常用的方法函数，具体的方法API也可以参考官方文档（<a href=\"http://www.trirand.com/jqgridwiki/doku.php?id=wiki:methods\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; color: rgb(51, 102, 153); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; word-break: break-all;\">http://www.trirand.com/jqgridwiki/doku.php?id=wiki:methods</a>&nbsp;）</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; font-weight: 700; word-break: break-all;\">1. getGridParam</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: Arial;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: Arial;\">这个方法用来获得jqGrid的选项值。它具有一个可选参数name，name即代表着jqGrid的选项名，例如：<br/></p><p><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; font-weight: 700; word-break: break-all;\">[javascript]</span>&nbsp;<a title=\"view plain\" class=\"ViewSource\" href=\"http://blog.csdn.net/gengv/article/details/5716347#\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; color: rgb(160, 160, 160); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; background-image: url(&quot;https://csdnimg.cn/release/phoenix/images/ico_plain.gif&quot;); background-position: left top; background-size: initial; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-color: inherit; border: none; padding: 1px; margin: 0px 10px 0px 0px; word-break: break-all; display: inline-block; width: 16px; height: 16px; text-indent: -2000px;\">view plain</a><a title=\"copy\" class=\"CopyToClipboard\" href=\"http://blog.csdn.net/gengv/article/details/5716347#\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; color: rgb(160, 160, 160); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; background-image: url(&quot;https://csdnimg.cn/release/phoenix/images/ico_copy.gif&quot;); background-position: left top; background-size: initial; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-color: inherit; border: none; padding: 1px; margin: 0px 10px 0px 0px; word-break: break-all; display: inline-block; width: 16px; height: 16px; text-indent: -2000px;\">copy</a></p><ol class=\"dp-c list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-bottom: 1px; margin-left: 45px; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; border: none; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(92, 92, 92); word-break: break-all;\"><li><p><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: inherit;\"><span class=\"keyword\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; color: rgb(0, 102, 153); background-color: inherit; font-weight: bold;\">var</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; background-color: inherit;\">&nbsp;id&nbsp;=&nbsp;$(</span><span class=\"string\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; margin: 0px; 