x; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 153, 102);\">注：我测试了一下，这个方法对于设置jqGrid的caption选项似乎无效。大概因此有了setCaption方法。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: Arial;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: Arial;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; font-weight: 700; word-break: break-all;\">7. setGridWidth</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: Arial;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: Arial;\">为Grid动态地设定一个新的宽度。两个参数：</p><ul style=\"list-style-type: none;\" class=\" list-paddingleft-2\"><li><p><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 153);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; font-weight: 700; word-break: break-all;\">new_width</span>&nbsp;</span>：以px为单位的新宽度值；</p></li><li><p><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 153);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; font-weight: 700; word-break: break-all;\">shrink</span>&nbsp;</span>：作用与jqGrid的shrinkToFit选项相同；如果此参数未设置，则沿用jqGrid的shrinkToFit选项的值。</p></li></ul><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: Arial;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; font-weight: 700; word-break: break-all;\">8. trigger(&quot;reloadGrid&quot;)</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: Arial;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: Arial;\">根据当前设置，重新载入Grid表格，即意味着向Server发送一个新的请求。此方法只能用于已经构建好的Grid。此外，此方法不会使对colModel所做出的改变生